where are you from originally?

1217
01:20:37,687 --> 01:20:38,949
- Oh, I moved.
- You moved?

1218
01:20:39,055 --> 01:20:41,421
Yeah. Originally I come from
Newark, New Jersey.

1219
01:20:41,524 --> 01:20:42,923
That's my hometown.

1220
01:20:43,025 --> 01:20:44,686
