I was just a kid.

1221
01:20:44,794 --> 01:20:46,489
- I think I was...
- How old were you?

1222
01:20:46,596 --> 01:20:49,224
- Oh, about sisteen years old.
- Sisteen?

1223
01:20:49,332 --> 01:20:52,324
- Like before. Fourteen, fifteen, sisteen.
- Sisteen. Yeah, sure.

1224
01:20:52,435 --> 01:20:54,096
Well, who was your toughest fight?

